column2: Inkfruit Women Adam & God Black T-shirt
column21:
• Product Description
  • Product Details

  • Composition
    Black round neck t-shirt made of 100% cotton with graphic on the front

    Wash care
    1. Light machine wash
    2. Do not bleach
    3. warm iron on reverse
    4. Do not dry clean
    5. Dry flat/reverse
    6. Do not scrub

    Fitting
    Comfort Fit

    If you are a music lover then you probably believe that God said "Let there be music" right after he said "Let there be light". This black tee from inkfruit will get your musical juices flowing. Team it with jeans or cargoes and add on a pair of stylish footwear now available exclusively at myntra.

    2. Height-5.7"
